      <description/>
      <pubDate>Mon, 29 Jun 2026 14:35:00 +0000</pubDate>
      <content:encoded>계란말이를 만들 때 계란 푼 물에 마요네즈를 한 스푼 넣어보자. 식감이 촉촉하고 부드러워진다. 고소한 풍미도 살아난다.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;figure&gt;&lt;img align="center" src="https://cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/chosun/XSVUCT5M4NFZVJAPYUTSFN5TRQ.jpg"&gt;&lt;figcaption&gt;&lt;small&gt;일러스트=김성규&lt;/small&gt;&lt;/figcaption&gt;&lt;/figure&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;</content:encoded>
    </item>
